# kuu.mbt is a local dependency resolved via workspace member.
# `just setup` creates the symlink (dev), or CI clones kawaz/kuu.mbt at the SHA-pinned commit
# into this same path (DR-0001 §2 Consequences). Either way the on-disk content is not tracked here.
/deps/kuu.mbt

# moon build output + registry cache (regenerated by `moon check` / `moon build`)
/_build
/cli/_build
/.mooncakes
